    "description": "<i>文明的黄昏降临，狂风肆虐全球。亚里亚斯的幸存者们纷纷逃入地下，寻求庇护。<br><br>在这危机四伏的世界里，你的父亲——费罗丁三世国王派出一支远征队，前往失落的堡垒之城利桑德亚。<br><br>据说，那里藏有一颗神奇的原始之种，能平息诸神的怒火，终结天空中肆虐的风暴。<br><br>你的兄长亲自率队远征，希望能寻回这件圣物，却从此杳无音讯。<br><br>不顾父亲的劝阻，你决心亲自前往利桑德亚一探究竟。<br><br>寻找失踪的兄长，夺回神圣的礼物，但要当心：这座古老的堡垒远非表面看起来那么简单……</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/908360/extras/c270a1e271bca0c76211c9f926b5d79c.poster.avif?t=1766432854\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/908360/extras/c270a1e271bca0c76211c9f926b5d79c.webm?t=1766432854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/908360/extras/a61a08bb212ce1322e02884d40d0678a.avif?t=1766432854\" width=600 height=66 /></span><br>《MONOMYTH》将为你呈现一个广阔而互通的游戏世界。从高耸入云的塔尖到幽深莫测的地窖，秘密房间、隐藏通道、风格迥异的区域，无不等待你的探索。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/908360/extras/53e09096a0297ca3895cde46d601eb32.avif?t=1766432854\" width=600 height=66 /></span><br>在这个精彩纷呈的地下世界中，你将遇到各种物品、谜题、怪物和形形色色的居民。通过独特的关键词对话系统与角色交流，灵活运用物品与环境互动。交易、撬锁、破门、掷物，甚至烘焙美味的面包，一切皆有可能！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/908360/extras/f3b6d2978c3d40d58675cf0bf220c327.avif?t=1766432854\" width=600 height=66 /></span><br>战斗系统丰富多样：挥剑、施法、闪避、招架、格挡，尽情施展你的战斗技巧。丰富的武器和强大的魔法任你使用，畅快体验战斗的乐趣。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/908360/extras/824c66382e6dc493875d460edc0cf932.avif?t=1766432854\" width=600 height=66 /></span><br>《MONOMYTH》可让你自由构建独特的角色。角色的六大属性、十三种技能任你搭配，解锁数十种不同的游戏风格。敏捷的刺客、强大的战斗法师，或是别具一格的全新职业，由你来定义！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/908360/extras/9d38dfd3b4c07138eb45c40bb2932303.avif?t=1766432854\" width=600 height=66 /></span><br>末日奇幻背景的《MONOMYTH》将魔法与科技完美融合，带你进入一个前所未见的独特世界。穿越黑暗诡谲的领域，迎战可怕的怪物，揭开利桑德亚堡垒之城的重重谜团。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/908360/extras/3db95fccb4c21f3dc40b728c2e267419.poster.avif?t=1766432854\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/908360/extras/3db95fccb4c21f3dc40b728c2e267419.webm?t=1766432854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
